      <title>阿布扎比就价值 220 亿美元的埃及优质土地交易进行高级谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/abu-dhabi-in-advanced-talks-on-22-billion-prime-egypt-land-deal-lsd8wp2v</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比正在就购买和开发埃及北部海岸的优质土地进行深入谈判，这项潜在的价值数十亿美元的交易将提振这个北非国家陷入困境的经济，并有助于缓解其外汇危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/abu-dhabi-in-advanced-talks-on-22-billion-prime-egypt-land-deal-lsd8wp2v</guid>
